    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a well-sorted A80 chassis powered by the legendary 2JZ-GTE twin-turbocharged 3.0L inline-six. This unit retains its factory sequential turbocharger array, providing a broad powerband and characteristic linear boost. Power is routed through the robust Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory Torsen limited-slip differential. The suspension maintains its original double-wishbone configuration, offering precise lateral stability. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive timing belt service and fresh valve cover gaskets to ensure optimal vacuum and compression. This is a mechanically rigorous example, perfect for an enthusiast seeking a true driver-spec Supra with a solid powertrain foundation and authentic feedback.",
